  schema:name "The Office as Normative Presheaf: Fiber Doctrine, Roman Law, and Constitutional Opposition" ;
  schema:description "The formal model of office as a normative presheaf with nuclear doctrine — fiber Heyting algebras, the munus/honor/dignitas trinity from Roman law, Kantorowicz's body politic, and Madison's separation of powers as nuclear insulation." ;
